object.script:
FUEL_UNEVEN = 1.0
function onTick() local leftFuel = input.getNumber(1) local rightFuel = input.getNumber(2) local pumpIn = input.getBool(1) and not input.getBool(2) local pumpOut = input.getBool(2) and not input.getBool(1) local neitherPump = not (pumpIn or pumpOut) local leftLow = (rightFuel - leftFuel) > FUEL_UNEVEN local rightLow = (leftFuel - rightFuel) > FUEL_UNEVEN
local leftPump = (neitherPump and leftLow) or (pumpIn and not rightLow) local leftValve = rightLow or (pumpOut and not leftLow) local rightPump = (neitherPump and rightLow) or (pumpIn and not leftLow) local rightValve = leftLow or (pumpOut and not rightLow)
output.setBool(1, pumpOut) output.setBool(2, pumpIn) output.setBool(3, leftPump) output.setBool(4, leftValve) output.setBool(5, rightPump) output.setBool(6, rightValve) end
